  "denoised_question": "<denoised_question>A beaver walks from (0,0) to (4,4) in the plane. At each step, he moves one unit in the positive x direction or one unit in the positive y direction, and he never goes to a point (x, y) where y > x. How many different paths can he walk?</denoised_question>",
