  "solution_steps": "Step 1: Evaluate the multiplication: 8 × 6 = 48. Step 2: Evaluate the division: 4 ÷ 2 = 2. Step 3: Subtract the result of the division from the result of the multiplication: 48 - 2 = 46.",
